es/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4426f86bd69c8bec9921f88ed2f56d828506b4","tid":520080,"uid":52881,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d42128544e56dce5e3f2c1d0f831a3ea782671e3","tid":520080,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9578542e85bde20f625e438649729e70f30f4e49","tid":520080,"uid":14816,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"應該係話比完賽仲留喺tvb個班就有陣柒味<br />\n永遠都好似小丑咁 <br />\n喺tvb就一線，一出到去即刻變二三線<br />\n有啲甚至走去拍劇做主持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又甘願俾人投閒置散<br />\n<br />\n相反肯出去搏下<br />\n好似許廷鏗小巧個啲反而幾欣賞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:13:17.000Z","msg":"削骨、牙mag個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"Mag同羅力威兩大台柱一齊埋葬左喺隻egg入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20c3242ce010f7d2d2dec738f8f965be1ae3d6e","tid":520080,"uid":14686,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家嘅許廷鏗都叫靚仔？？<br />\n佢起碼要減10磅啦<br />\n<br />\n佢唱歌其實都唔掂<br />\n係學歷同牙醫身份令佢有市場<br />\n削骨唱歌好聽過佢</blockquote>佢唱歌其實真係還好<br />\n但佢開頭已經多產 令好多人識<br />\n到後來又肯周圍去搵唔同班底創作 <br />\n唔會淨係用TVB 嘅張美賢張家誠<br />\n<br />\n尤其新碟作品真係好高質<br />\n但唱功必須加強<br />\n但真係好欣賞佢嘅主見同夠膽為咗自己嘅音樂而離開星夢<br />\n<br />\n我只可以講 仲留係TVB 個班星夢都唔係真心熱愛音樂熱愛歌手呢個職業<br />\n我唔相信會有真係熱愛音樂嘅人甘心一世淨係唱口水歌k 歌或主題曲<br />\n係星夢連想同唔同音樂人合作嘅機會都冇</blockquote>可能其他都係想走嘅,俾張約綁住姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後庭都算呢班中間比較早有合約,始終比賽嗰期叫最靚仔,又後生又唱得下<br />\n唔唱歌都可以返去讀埋個牙醫,讀滿書唱片公司又驚你唔簽,議價能力高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做極紅唔起的話,TVB梗係開埋D垃圾約俾你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算佢宜家唔唱歌 全職做牙醫都搵到食<br />\n再加埋屋企都中產 可以全心做音樂無經濟負擔 係唔同啲既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b34d7b830233455e8a2ebeb985341c59b793292","tid":520080,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e7dc7412fb1e3a26b41a3763e6a7c0373be750","tid":520080,"uid":3933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e44024054e34786912ff4ade8063888df59b5122","tid":520080,"uid":56716,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對眼咁撚柒都叫靚仔</blockquote><br />\n許廷鏗都叫柒唔通連登仔叫靚仔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:12:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/p53395go110.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fp53395go110.gif&h=e051c4e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b322e5762ef110695b600230c4ddbcdaba6655d","tid":520080,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>對眼咁撚柒都叫靚仔</blockquote><br />\n許廷鏗都叫柒唔通連登仔叫靚仔？</blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/p53395go110.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fp53395go110.gif&h=e051c4e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係等緊你入嚟貼呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925a9cda168d642f713dcb5959374e6ec6b9d0c0","tid":5