id":520080,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>許廷鏗勁靚仔囉，佢有種公子嘅貴氣，係而家肥咗啫。</blockquote><br />\n性格幾好 同欣宜勁fd<br />\n見佢成日好就欣宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d5ce7ba6389d4837c5f630a0a631009e392402","tid":520080,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56e0f8954f0c5417089f29c3c85640af208d4201","tid":520080,"uid":72195,"like":241,"dislike":7,"score":234,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"其實許廷鏗幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樣唔差，有學識，真係做音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歌都唔會只係情歌，又做到每年一hit song<br />\n螞蟻，面具，青春頌，神奇之旅，仲有好多歌都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左成日比人話gay之外，都無咩負面新聞，雖然我唔明gay唔gay同聽歌有乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但反而吳業坤，胡仲多人討論，完全唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"佢之前因為轉會俾人雪成半年啫，之後應該會紅返"},{"pid":"4fceb4e6f93efaad7547c81f06927815cd1ad296","tid":520080,"uid":34427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係話比完賽仲留喺tvb個班就有陣柒味<br />\n永遠都好似小丑咁 <br />\n喺tvb就一線，一出到去即刻變二三線<br />\n有啲甚至走去拍劇做主持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又甘願俾人投閒置散<br />\n<br />\n相反肯出去搏下<br />\n好似許廷鏗小巧個啲反而幾欣賞</blockquote><br />\n許廷鏗出走後歌路其實幾清幾有個人特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋小巧配藍奕邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而周柏豪變左要用tvb御用班底 首歌同其他劇集歌一色一樣 但tvb自己頒獎禮都係幫佢放曬煙花 得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小巧啲歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8498ff8099cc896fd57ce3623237795c8ad3187","tid":520080,"uid":34427,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但胡紅釣唱歌真係好佢好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望本尊浸多陣tvb 有知名度就轉會啦<br />\n叱咤睇後台訪問 見佢話4年後有得參加返叱咤好夢幻好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d25db7ba65b1975a815c6422cbf086dce6fafdb","tid":520080,"uid":80566,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"03a3eebe4a9f402731857924f060bce1f9707439","tid":520080,"uid":35701,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"cce11b429f32c43462ad0839cb932e7c38c66567","tid":520080,"uid":52881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"44da656283b2f7ba7ef066b3cdb7ba7cf860a65b","tid":520080,"uid":35701,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"可能其他都係想走嘅,俾張約綁住姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後庭都算呢班中間比較早有合約,始終比賽嗰期叫最靚仔,又後生又唱得下<br />\n唔唱歌都可以返去讀埋個牙醫,讀滿書唱片公司又驚你唔簽,議價能力高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做極紅唔起的話,TVB梗係開埋D垃圾約俾你"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"同意胡鴻鈞似真係想搞音樂<br />\n佢新碟都有兩三隻歌係完全脫離tvb班底<br />\n佢都有話過如果有機會開音樂會想唱多啲自己嘅歌 唔想個concert變左經典電視劇主題曲之夜<br />\n但始終係因為降魔的紅 我諗佢想走都有一定難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b20a58d29476994eb1d919fc9aeb80085696bbe","tid":520080,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能其他都係想走嘅,俾張約綁住姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後庭都算呢班中間比較早有合約,始終比賽嗰期叫最靚仔,又後生又唱得下<br />\n唔唱歌都可以返去讀埋個牙醫,讀滿書唱片公司又驚你唔簽,議價能力高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做極紅唔起的話,TVB梗係開埋D垃圾約俾你</blockquote>你望吓何雁詩呢班 邊到似真係想搞好音樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胡鴻鈞好似想走就係真嘅</blockquote>走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友啱啱開始多產拍劇，唔覺佢有幾想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>如果你真係想唱歌嘅就算佢俾埋你做男主角你都想走架啦<br />\n不過都係之前睇報紙定咩睇到<br />\n真唔真就唔知了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都幾可悲<br />\n一班「應該」好鐘意唱歌而去參加歌唱節目嘅人<br />\n但最尾大部份都冇得唱歌<br />\n譚嘉儀同一首歌拎兩個獎 <br />\n而個首仲要係翻唱歌 陪著你走<br />\n<br />\n孖仔好似完全冇出過歌添<br />\n仲有個咩將軍澳吳尊？(唔記得佢叫咩名<br />\n有份去天與地爬雪山個個)<br />\n又係 好似都冇唱過歌 反而主持拍戲都有人識</blockquote><br />\n將軍澳吳尊係許廷鏗，天與地爬雪山嗰個係謝東閔，外號一廠黎明。"},{"pid":"ca2f241a8166c86d1e832d2efe9821cb9616f883","tid":520080,"uid":35193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"後廷轉咗公司已經算叫做摵甩咗巨星幫果道柒氣啦"},{"pid":"69b40b77528fd081f3f1d2640370cfa1b95fb7a0","tid":520080,"uid":160833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"牙醫d歌真係唔錯<br />\n星夢其他就<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14dc38bf74d76bed3b388ca914ce798a6d96c981","tid":520080,"uid":165439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打揾到削骨參加巨星時個樣 想整個對比照 上網好難揾"},{"pid":"3398e551024c6f4d3a3fdcebf802dbf04c0bf6b6","tid":520080,"uid":17622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"正如公屋仔一樣"},{"pid":"7b552eff731487e2a8a18ec8f16efd22b8b55185","tid":520080,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11f9cddc4e0c9c6d6d10f3b1ca86b89c1e41d361","tid":520080,"uid":50776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"14dc38bf74d76bed3b388ca914ce798a6d96c981","tid":520080,"uid":165439,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打揾到削骨參加巨星時個樣 想整個對比照 上網好難揾"},"citedBy